1
00:00:08,491 --> 00:00:10,994
[ Chattering ]

2
00:00:32,632 --> 00:00:35,935
[ Door Opens, Closes ]

3
00:00:38,438 --> 00:00:41,274
[ Man On TV ]
NOW THIS-- THIS HERE'S
A SPECIAL NUMBER.

4
00:00:41,274 --> 00:00:45,195
IT'S GONNA MAKE YOUR TONGUE
ROLL OUTTA YOUR HEAD
AND DIAL 911.

5
00:00:45,695 --> 00:00:47,947
[ TV: Laughter ]

6
00:00:53,803 --> 00:00:55,722
[ TV: Indistinct ]

7
00:01:06,399 --> 00:01:08,234
[ Garbled Shouts ]

8
00:01:11,004 --> 00:01:14,240
YOU ADD IN
ALL THAT NICE SHRIMP--
[ Gasps ]

9
00:01:24,451 --> 00:01:26,770
[ Man On Police Radio ]
DISPATCH, THIS IS UNIT 7...

10
00:01:26,770 --> 00:01:29,773
INVESTIGATING
A REPORT OF DISTURBANCE
AT 214 PROSPECT AVENUE, OVER.

11
00:01:29,773 --> 00:01:31,858
[ Female Dispatcher ]
COPY THAT, UNIT 7.

12
00:01:43,586 --> 00:01:45,088
JEEZ.

13
00:01:52,846 --> 00:01:56,049
POLICE !  DON'T MOVE.

14
00:02:01,771 --> 00:02:04,240
KEEP 'EM IN THE AIR.

15
00:02:06,926 --> 00:02:09,095
CUFF HER, JIMMY.

16
00:02:10,346 --> 00:02:13,049
DAMN, SHE'S GOT
BLOOD ALL OVER HER.

17
00:02:16,886 --> 00:02:18,888
HEY, KEITH.

18
00:02:18,888 --> 00:02:21,724
I THINK YOU MIGHT WANNA
CHECK THIS OUT.

19
00:02:29,315 --> 00:02:31,985
I THINK SHE'S BLIND.

20
00:03:24,086 --> 00:03:28,423
THE DECEASED IS PACO ORDONEZ,
A.K.A. LITTLE MONSTER--

21
00:03:28,423 --> 00:03:31,927
STREET DEALER, LIKED TO USE
GRADE-SCHOOL KIDS AS COURIERS.

22
00:03:31,927 --> 00:03:34,930
OUT ON BAIL FOR POSSESSION
WITH INTENT.

23
00:03:34,930 --> 00:03:37,432
TWO-TIME LOSER
LOOKING AT LIFE.

24
00:03:37,432 --> 00:03:40,435
I HAVE THE SAME
PAIR OF PANTS.

25
00:03:40,435 --> 00:03:42,437
WHO EXTERMINATED HIM ?

26
00:03:43,939 --> 00:03:46,441
THAT'S A SUBJECT
OF SOME DEBATE.

27
00:03:48,143 --> 00:03:51,480
THE KILLER CARVED A SINGLE
C-SHAPED CUT UP THROUGH
THE RIGHT KIDNEY.

28
00:03:51,980 --> 00:03:54,349
FATAL BLOOD LOSS CAME
IN UNDER 30 SECONDS.

29
00:03:54,349 --> 00:03:58,787
I'M GOING TO ASSUME THE KILLER
KNEW WHAT HE WAS DOING, AND THAT
"C" WASN'T ONE OF HIS INITIALS.

30
00:03:59,288 --> 00:04:02,574
YOUR ASSUMPTIONS ARE CORRECT,
ONLY THE KILLER ISN'T A HE.

31
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:09,982
MARTY GLENN, 28.

32
00:04:09,982 --> 00:04:13,001
WE FOUND HER AT THE SCENE
DOING A FORMULA 409.

33
00:04:13,001 --> 00:04:17,623
UNDER NORMAL CIRCUMSTANCES,
MY DEPARTMENT WOULD HAVE HER
DEAD TO RIGHTS.

34
00:04:17,623 --> 00:04:21,910
THERE'S JUST
ONE LITTLE SNAG.
SHE'S BEEN
BLIND SINCE BIRTH.

35
00:04:21,910 --> 00:04:25,631
BEFORE YOUR HEART
GOES OUT TO HER,
CHECK OUT HER RAP SHEET.

36
00:04:25,631 --> 00:04:30,052
FRAUD, PETTY THEFT,
AGGRAVATED ASSAULT.

37
00:04:30,052 --> 00:04:33,355
BELIEVE ME,
SHE'S A REAL PIECE OF WORK.

38
00:04:33,355 --> 00:04:36,291
HER JUVENILE RECORDS ARE SEALED,
BUT DETECTIVE PENNOCK
HAS IT ON AUTHORITY...

39
00:04:36,291 --> 00:04:40,629
THAT TWO OF THEM WERE
DRUG BUSTS-- POSSESSION
AND POSSESSION WITH INTENT.

40
00:04:40,629 --> 00:04:46,368
SO DO YOU THINK THAT SHE CAUGHT
LITTLE MONSTER TRYING TO SNATCH
THE PEBBLE FROM HER HAND ?

41
00:04:46,368 --> 00:04:48,470
NOTHING ELSE MAKES SENSE.

42
00:04:48,470 --> 00:04:51,857
INCLUDING HOW A BLIND GIRL COULD
GET THE DROP ON AN EX-CON...

43
00:04:51,857 --> 00:04:54,326
AND BLEED HIM OUT
WITH SURGICAL PRECISION.

44
00:04:54,826 --> 00:04:57,829
MS. GLENN TOOK A $60 CAB RIDE
ALONE STRAIGHT TO THE MOTEL.

45
00:04:57,829 --> 00:05:00,832
THE CABBIE INSTRUCTED HER TO
ROOM 10, WHICH SHE ASKED FOR
SPECIFICALLY...

46
00:05:01,333 --> 00:05:03,335
AND THEN TOLD HIM
TO GET LOST.

47
00:05:03,335 --> 00:05:05,337
THIRTY MINUTES LATER,
DEAD HEROIN DEALER.

48
00:05:05,337 --> 00:05:09,658
ALL RIGHT, SO YOU REALLY BELIEVE
THAT SHE DID THIS,

49
00:05:09,658 --> 00:05:11,493
YOU JUST DON'T KNOW HOW.

50
00:05:11,493 --> 00:05:15,213
I GOT A THEORY
IF YOU WANT TO HEAR IT.

51
00:05:16,548 --> 00:05:20,519
I THINK SHE'S GOT
SOME KINDA SIXTH SENSE--

52
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:23,805
LETS HER SEE IN THE DARK,
LIKE A BAT OR SOMETHING.

53
00:05:25,374 --> 00:05:28,210
I GOT 48 HOURS
TO CONVINCE THE D.A.,

54
00:05:28,210 --> 00:05:31,613
OR WAIT TILL SHE KILLS
SOMEBODY ELSE.

55
00:05:33,098 --> 00:05:34,967
HOW SOON CAN I MEET HER ?

56
00:05:34,967 --> 00:05:37,703
[ Cell Door Sliding ]

57
00:05:37,703 --> 00:05:41,556
[ Footsteps ]
OH...

58
00:05:41,556 --> 00:05:43,392
IT'S YOU.

59
00:05:43,392 --> 00:05:45,294
SEE WHAT I MEAN ?

60
00:05:45,794 --> 00:05:48,297
IT'S NOT MAGIC.
 IT'S YOUR CRAPPY COLOGNE.

61
00:05:49,798 --> 00:05:51,800
WHO'S THAT WITH YOU ?

62
00:05:52,801 --> 00:05:55,654
- SPECIAL AGENT MULDER.
- AND THE LADY ?

63
00:05:57,556 --> 00:06:01,860
UH, SPECIAL AGENT SCULLY.
WE'D LIKE TO ASK YOU
SOME QUESTIONS, MARTY.

64
00:06:01,860 --> 00:06:05,998
YOU MUST BE HAVING TROUBLE
WITH YOUR CASE, DETECTIVE.

65
00:06:11,086 --> 00:06:13,088
FINE.
SUIT YOURSELF.

66
00:06:21,596 --> 00:06:23,098
WHAT ARE YOU STARING AT ?

67
00:06:23,598 --> 00:06:26,601
AN INNOCENT WOMAN--
I HOPE.

68
00:06:37,846 --> 00:06:40,849
SO, I'M ALL EARS.

69
00:06:40,849 --> 00:06:44,236
I'M CURIOUS WHY YOU'VE
REFUSED YOUR RIGHT
TO AN ATTORNEY.

70
00:06:44,820 --> 00:06:48,323
UNLESS YOU'RE GONNA CHARGE ME,
I DON'T PLAN ON NEEDING ONE.

71
00:06:48,323 --> 00:06:50,325
WELL, YOU COULD BE
CHARGED RIGHT NOW,

72
00:06:50,325 --> 00:06:55,247
WITH THE FACT THAT YOU'VE GIVEN
NO COMPELLING REASON WHY
YOU WERE IN THAT MOTEL ROOM.

73
00:06:55,247 --> 00:06:57,249
WHAT WERE YOU
DOING THERE, MARTY ?

74
00:06:59,251 --> 00:07:01,253
PUTTING MINTS
ON THE PILLOWS.

75
00:07:04,456 --> 00:07:08,960
THE CABBIE HAS GIVEN A STATEMENT
THAT YOU ASKED SPECIFICALLY
FOR ROOM 10,

76
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:11,847
WHICH WOULD PUT YOU
AT THE MURDER SCENE
RIGHT ABOUT THE TIME OF DEATH.

77
00:07:11,847 --> 00:07:15,317
IS THAT A CRIME ?
IF YOU WERE INVOLVED
IN ANY WAY.

78
00:07:15,317 --> 00:07:18,403
YOU MEAN, LIKE,
AN EYEWITNESS ?

79
00:07:18,403 --> 00:07:21,907
DID YOU INTEND TO BUY DRUGS
FROM PACO ORDONEZ ?

80
00:07:26,728 --> 00:07:29,030
DID YOU KILL HIM ?

81
00:07:29,030 --> 00:07:31,967
MAYBE IT WAS JUST
HIS TIME TO GO.

82
00:07:31,967 --> 00:07:35,070
OTHER THAN THE STAB WOUND,
DID YOU CHECK HIS
CHOLESTEROL LEVEL OR ANYTHING ?

83
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:37,072
HOW DID YOU KNOW THERE WAS
JUST ONE STAB WOUND ?

84
00:07:37,072 --> 00:07:40,509
DID I SAY THAT ?
MM-HMM.

85
00:07:40,509 --> 00:07:42,911
I GUESSED.

86
00:07:43,412 --> 00:07:46,832
YOU KNOW WHAT THE PROBLEM IS ?
YOU'VE GOT NO MURDER WEAPON.

87
00:07:48,717 --> 00:07:51,536
AND I BET THAT'S DRIVIN'
STINKY BACK THERE CRAZY.

88
00:07:51,536 --> 00:07:53,822
ISN'T IT, STINKY ?

89
00:07:53,822 --> 00:07:58,126
WHY IS HE HIDING ?
IT'S NOT LIKE I CAN SEE HIM.

90
00:07:58,126 --> 00:08:02,881
YOU KNOW WHAT I DID
WITH IT, DETECTIVE ?
I FED IT TO MY SEEING EYE DOG.

91
00:08:02,881 --> 00:08:06,384
I'M CURIOUS, MARTY.
YEAH ?  ABOUT WHAT ?

92
00:08:06,384 --> 00:08:09,354
IF YOU DIDN'T KILL HIM,
WHY YOU WERE AT THE CRIME SCENE
CLEANING UP...

93
00:08:09,354 --> 00:08:11,857
AND DOING SUCH
A PISS-POOR JOB OF IT ?

94
00:08:14,059 --> 00:08:16,428
WHY DON'T WE JUST STOP
PLAYING GAMES HERE, OKAY ?

95
00:08:16,428 --> 00:08:20,148
I MEAN, YOU PROBABLY
DON'T KNOW A FEATHER DUSTER
FROM A DUCK'S ASS, DO YA ?

96
00:08:20,148 --> 00:08:23,618
I MEAN, IT'S RIDICULOUS.
YOU'RE A BLIND WOMAN,
FOR GOD'S SAKE.

97
00:08:23,618 --> 00:08:26,354
SO WHY DON'T YOU TELL US
WHO DID KILL PACO ORDONEZ,

98
00:08:26,855 --> 00:08:29,858
AND AGENT SCULLY AND I
CAN GO ARREST HIM...

99
00:08:29,858 --> 00:08:33,245
AND YOU CAN GO HOME AND WORK ON
YOUR "ANGRY YOUNG BLIND GIRL"
COMEDY ROUTINE.

100
00:08:37,766 --> 00:08:42,504
OR WE CAN JUST STAY HERE
AND ENTERTAIN EACH OTHER
FOR THE NEXT 48 HOURS.

101
00:08:42,504 --> 00:08:46,141
[ Glass Clatters ]

102
00:08:47,542 --> 00:08:49,544
GO TO HELL.

103
00:08:50,412 --> 00:08:52,881
[ Pennock ]
SEE WHAT I MEAN ?

104
00:08:53,882 --> 00:08:56,384
PUT A KNIFE IN THAT HAND--
NO.

105
00:08:56,384 --> 00:09:00,388
ALL I SEE IS A WOMAN
WHO'S ADAPTED TO HER
IMPAIRMENT ADMIRABLY.

106
00:09:00,388 --> 00:09:04,192
SHE'S HONED ALL HER OTHER
SENSES AROUND HER BLINDNESS.
SHE'S TAUNTING YOU.

107
00:09:04,192 --> 00:09:07,479
I DON'T KNOW.  I THINK SHE
JUST WANTS US TO THINK THAT
SHE'S STRONG, INDEPENDENT.

108
00:09:07,479 --> 00:09:10,982
- IT'S IMPORTANT TO HER.
-SHE WANTS US TO KNOW
 SHE DID IT.

109
00:09:10,982 --> 00:09:15,303
- I DON'T THINK SHE DID DO IT.
- THEN WHY WON'T SHE HELP US ?

110
00:09:15,303 --> 00:09:20,291
IT'S BEEN MY EXPERIENCE
THAT INNOCENT PEOPLE DON'T
ACT LIKE THAT, AGENT MULDER.

111
00:09:20,291 --> 00:09:23,111
SHE WOULDN'T EXPLAIN
HER PRESENCE AT THE CRIME SCENE,

112
00:09:23,111 --> 00:09:26,114
AND SHE AVOIDED ALL DISCUSSION
ABOUT THE MURDER WEAPON.

113
00:09:26,114 --> 00:09:28,016
SHE KNEW THERE WAS
ONLY ONE STAB WOUND.

114
00:09:28,016 --> 00:09:31,036
YOU CAUGHT THAT YOURSELF.
YEAH.

115
00:09:31,036 --> 00:09:33,204
DETECTIVE, DID YOU SNAKE
ALL OF THE PLUMBING
IN THE BATHROOM ?

116
00:09:33,204 --> 00:09:35,957
I TURNED THAT PLACE
UPSIDE DOWN AND INSIDE OUT.

117
00:09:35,957 --> 00:09:41,329
WELL, IF WE FIND THE WEAPON
WITH HER FINGERPRINTS ON IT,
SHE'S AS GOOD AS CONVICTED.

118
00:09:41,329 --> 00:09:43,214
SHORT OF THAT,
SHE'S GONNA WALK.

119
00:09:43,214 --> 00:09:46,951
MAYBE I CAN GET YOU TO
COME OUT TO THE CRIME SCENE
ONE LAST TIME.

120
00:09:46,951 --> 00:09:49,037
OKAY.

121
00:09:49,037 --> 00:09:53,658
YOU GO AHEAD.  I WANNA--
I WANNA INVESTIGATE SOMETHING.

122
00:09:54,826 --> 00:09:57,395
[ Door Opens ]

123
00:10:00,715 --> 00:10:02,467
[ Door Closes ]

124
00:10:02,467 --> 00:10:06,221
[ Man ]
I'M GOING TO ASK YOU
A SERIES OF QUESTIONS.

125
00:10:06,221 --> 00:10:08,723
RESPOND ONLY WITH
A "YES" OR "NO."

126
00:10:08,723 --> 00:10:11,726
DO NOT JUDGE THE CONTENT
OF THE QUESTIONS.
SIMPLY ANSWER TRUTHFULLY.

127
00:10:14,229 --> 00:10:16,481
IS YOUR FULL NAME
MARTELL FRANCIS GLENN ?
YEAH.

128
00:10:16,481 --> 00:10:20,068
ARE YOU A RESIDENT
OF THE STATE OF DELAWARE ?

129
00:10:20,568 --> 00:10:23,888
LET'S CUT THROUGH THE BULL,
OR I'M GONNA DECIDE
NOT TO COOPERATE AT ALL.

130
00:10:23,888 --> 00:10:27,325
ALL RIGHT,
LET'S, UH, GET TO IT.

131
00:10:27,325 --> 00:10:29,561
I NEED TO ESTABLISH
A BASELINE.

132
00:10:30,061 --> 00:10:32,530
I'M A RESIDENT OF THE STATE
OF DELAWARE, OKAY ?

133
00:10:32,530 --> 00:10:34,532
LET'S MOVE ON.
[ Sighs ]

134
00:10:36,985 --> 00:10:39,821
IS IT YOUR INTENT TO LIE
DURING THE COURSE OF
THIS EXAMINATION ?

135
00:10:39,821 --> 00:10:41,973
I'M SURE YOU'LL
TELL ME IF IT IS.

136
00:10:44,342 --> 00:10:47,912
DID YOU STAB PACO ORDONEZ,
ALSO KNOWN AS LITTLE MONSTER ?

137
00:10:47,912 --> 00:10:50,098
NOPE.

138
00:10:53,301 --> 00:10:57,722
- DID YOU PLAN OR ARRANGE
  THE MURDER OF PACO ORDONEZ ?
- NO.

139
00:10:57,722 --> 00:11:00,225
HAVE YOU EVER MET
PACO ORDONEZ ?
NO.

140
00:11:00,225 --> 00:11:04,395
WOULD YOU EVER HAVE OCCASION
TO SEE PACO ORDONEZ
OR KNOW HIM IN ANOTHER WAY ?

141
00:11:06,164 --> 00:11:08,283
STRIKE THAT.

142
00:11:08,283 --> 00:11:12,670
HAVE YOU EVER HAD OCCASION
TO INTERACT WITH PACO ORDONEZ
OR KNOW HIM IN ANOTHER WAY ?

143
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:14,722
NO.

144
00:11:15,223 --> 00:11:18,293
-WERE YOU PRESENT DURING
  THE MURDER OF PACO ORDONEZ ?
- NO.

145
00:11:25,433 --> 00:11:28,369
WHY DON'T YOU JUST
ASK ME YOURSELF ?

146
00:11:29,871 --> 00:11:32,624
DID YOU SEE THE MURDER ?

147
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:37,395
DID YOU SEE THE MURDER ?

148
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:42,650
- I DON'T SEE ANYTHING.
-YES OR NO ONLY, PLEASE.

149
00:11:42,650 --> 00:11:44,969
THEN, THE ANSWER IS NO.

150
00:11:51,509 --> 00:11:54,846
[ Pennock ]
NO BLOOD TRAILS
LEADING OUT OF THE BATHROOM.

151
00:11:54,846 --> 00:11:56,848
WINDOWS ARE PAINTED SHUT.

152
00:11:59,350 --> 00:12:02,353
AS YOU CAN SEE,
NOT A LOT OF PLACES
SHE COULD'VE STASHED IT.

153
00:12:02,353 --> 00:12:04,355
[ Cell Phone Rings ]

154
00:12:07,859 --> 00:12:09,727
SCULLY.

155
00:12:09,727 --> 00:12:11,629
SHE'S LYING.
ABOUT WHAT ?

156
00:12:12,130 --> 00:12:15,633
SHE KNEW PACO ORDONEZ,
BUT I DON'T THINK
SHE MURDERED HIM.

157
00:12:15,633 --> 00:12:17,635
HOW DO YOU KNOW
THAT SHE KNEW HIM ?

158
00:12:17,635 --> 00:12:21,139
I MADE HER TAKE
A POLYGRAPH TEST.  SHE PASSED
ON EVERY QUESTION EXCEPT ONE:

159
00:12:21,639 --> 00:12:23,474
DID SHE SEE THE MURDER ?

160
00:12:23,474 --> 00:12:27,829
WOULD YOU LIKE ME TO
REMIND YOU WHY POLYGRAPHS
ARE INADMISSIBLE IN COURT ?

161
00:12:27,829 --> 00:12:30,865
NO, SHE CRACKED, SCULLY.
SHE WAS LYING.  I'M SURE OF IT.

162
00:12:31,366 --> 00:12:35,920
WELL, MAYBE SHE WAS, MULDER, BUT
DON'T MAKE ME STATE THE OBVIOUS.
SHE DIDN'T SEE ANYTHING.

163
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:38,756
NOT WITH HER EYES.
WELL, HOW ELSE
DID SHE SEE ?

164
00:12:38,756 --> 00:12:42,460
BAT VISION ?
I DON'T KNOW.

165
00:12:43,828 --> 00:12:46,631
WELL, MULDER, WHEN YOU
FIGURE IT OUT, GIVE ME A CALL.

166
00:12:47,131 --> 00:12:48,633
[ Beeps Off ]

167
00:13:03,498 --> 00:13:04,999
DETECTIVE PENNOCK ?

168
00:13:27,956 --> 00:13:30,058
[ Voice Garbled ]

169
00:13:39,751 --> 00:13:42,253
[ Gasps ]
SOMEBODY, I NEED A PHONE.

170
00:13:44,255 --> 00:13:48,009
I GET TO CALL A LAWYER !
SOMEBODY, I NEED A PHONE !

171
00:13:49,794 --> 00:13:51,679
I GOT IT.

172
00:13:57,085 --> 00:14:01,089
YOU KNOW, I'M SURE THE A.C.L.U.
IS GONNA BE VERY INTERESTED...

173
00:14:01,589 --> 00:14:04,092
IN HOW YOU VIOLATED
A BLIND WOMAN'S RIGHTS...

174
00:14:04,592 --> 00:14:08,196
BY EAVESDROPPING ON
HER PRIVATE PHONE CALL.

175
00:14:08,196 --> 00:14:10,081
SAME TO YOU.

176
00:14:15,453 --> 00:14:18,289
[ Ringing ]
dddd [ Blues ]

177
00:14:18,790 --> 00:14:21,376
BLARNEY STONE.

178
00:14:21,376 --> 00:14:25,179
UM, LET'S SEE--
THE GUY HITTIN' ON THE REDHEAD
AT THE END OF THE BAR.

179
00:14:25,179 --> 00:14:29,784
- I TOLD YOU, STOP IT !
- YEAH, WE GOT SOMEBODY
  MATCHING THAT DESCRIPTION.

180
00:14:33,137 --> 00:14:35,723
POP, IT'S FOR YOU.

181
00:14:41,729 --> 00:14:44,582
- YEAH ?
- LEAVE HER ALONE.

182
00:14:51,322 --> 00:14:53,074
WHO IS THIS ?

183
00:14:53,074 --> 00:14:55,343
YOU JUST LEAVE HER ALONE.

184
00:14:55,343 --> 00:14:57,795
I'M WATCHING YOU.

185
00:14:57,795 --> 00:15:00,298
[ Line Disconnects,
  Dial Tone ]

186
00:15:14,679 --> 00:15:17,014
LET ME GUESS.
YOUR KILLER IS O.J. SIMPSON.

187
00:15:17,014 --> 00:15:21,402
THEY WERE FOUND
AT THE CRIME SCENE
WITH BLOOD ALL OVER THEM.

188
00:15:21,402 --> 00:15:23,788
WE BELIEVE THEY WERE WORN
BY PACO ORDONEZ'S KILLER.

189
00:15:23,788 --> 00:15:26,040
HMM.  YOU'RE GOOD.

190
00:15:26,040 --> 00:15:29,410
WE THINK THEY
BELONG TO YOU.
WELL, THEY DON'T.

191
00:15:29,911 --> 00:15:33,247
TRY ONE ON FOR US.
AND PUT MY PRINTS
ALL OVER THEM ?

192
00:15:33,247 --> 00:15:35,450
YOUR PRINTS ARE ALREADY
ALL OVER THEM, MARTY.

193
00:15:38,870 --> 00:15:40,788
[ Pennock ]
HOLD STILL.

194
00:15:46,294 --> 00:15:48,129
ARE YOU HAPPY, DETECTIVE ?

195
00:15:48,129 --> 00:15:50,031
LOOKS TO ME LIKE IT FITS.

196
00:15:50,031 --> 00:15:55,486
SOMEWHERE MARCIA CLARK WEEPS.
BUT YOU STILL HAVEN'T
GOT A WEAPON.

197
00:15:55,486 --> 00:15:59,557
OH, IT'S JUST
A MATTER OF TIME.

198
00:15:59,557 --> 00:16:01,959
BUT YOU HAVEN'T GOT TIME.

199
00:16:03,845 --> 00:16:06,197
HOPE YOU SAW WHAT
JUST HAPPENED IN THERE.

200
00:16:06,197 --> 00:16:09,434
EVEN IF THE GLOVES DO FIT,
YOU CAN STILL ACQUIT.

201
00:16:09,934 --> 00:16:14,439
I THINK IT'S ARROGANCE.  I THINK
IT'S THE SAME REASON SHE AGREED
TO TAKE THE POLYGRAPH TEST.

202
00:16:14,439 --> 00:16:17,308
SHE KNOWS THAT
THE PREJUDICES IN THIS CASE
ARE ALL IN HER FAVOR.

203
00:16:17,308 --> 00:16:20,745
I DON'T THINK
IT'S THAT SIMPLE.
LOOK AT THIS.

204
00:16:20,745 --> 00:16:23,080
SHE LIVES IN POVERTY,
BUT SHE'S NEVER
TAKEN ADVANTAGE...

205
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:26,250
OF THE DISABILITY BENEFITS
THAT ARE AVAILABLE TO HER--
NEVER ONCE.

206
00:16:26,250 --> 00:16:29,137
IT'S POISON TO HER.
THE MERE SUGGESTION...

207
00:16:29,137 --> 00:16:32,640
THAT SHE'S ANYTHING OTHER THAN
A WHOLE OR COMPLETE PERSON
IS OFFENSIVE TO HER.

208
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:34,509
IT'S NOT ARROGANCE,
 IT'S PRIDE.

209
00:16:34,509 --> 00:16:38,463
YOU THINK IT WAS PRIDE
THAT MADE HER DITCH
THE BLOODY GLOVES ?

210
00:16:38,963 --> 00:16:41,265
HER PRINTS WERE
ALL OVER THEM, MULDER.
WHY WOULD SHE DO THAT ?

211
00:16:41,265 --> 00:16:45,069
I HAVE NO IDEA.
OKAY, SO BY
YOUR REASONING,

212
00:16:45,069 --> 00:16:48,289
THE KILLER TOOK OFF
WITH THE MURDER WEAPON
BUT NOT THE GLOVES,

213
00:16:48,289 --> 00:16:51,292
LEAVING MARTY TO COME IN,
GO STRAIGHT TO THE GLOVES,

214
00:16:51,292 --> 00:16:54,295
AND HIDE THEM IN THE ONE PLACE
THAT NOBODY WOULD EASILY THINK
TO FIND THEM.

215
00:16:54,295 --> 00:16:58,616
I THINK THAT'S
THE MOST ACCURATE SCENARIO
AVAILABLE TO US RIGHT NOW.

216
00:17:00,501 --> 00:17:02,803
WAIT A MINUTE.
MAYBE IT'S MUCH
SIMPLER THAN THAT.

217
00:17:02,803 --> 00:17:04,972
WHAT ?

218
00:17:06,274 --> 00:17:08,526
WHAT IF SHE'S NOT
REALLY BLIND ?

219
00:17:08,526 --> 00:17:12,430
I MEAN, SHE HASN'T
APPLIED FOR ANY OF HER
DISABILITY BENEFITS.

220
00:17:12,430 --> 00:17:15,399
MAYBE THAT'S BECAUSE
SHE KNOWS SHE COULDN'T PASS
THE MEDICAL SCREENING.

221
00:17:15,399 --> 00:17:19,187
- YOU THINK SHE'S FAKING IT ?
- NO.

222
00:17:19,187 --> 00:17:22,190
NO, BUT POSSIBLY IT'S
A CONVERSION DISORDER...

223
00:17:22,190 --> 00:17:26,694
OR A FORM OF BLIND SIGHT--
A SPLIT CONSCIOUSNESS,
WHEREBY A PERSON HAS...

224
00:17:26,694 --> 00:17:30,865
A CERTAIN LEVEL OF VISUAL
ABILITY, BUT THEY'RE NOT AWARE
THEY'RE ACTUALLY SEEING.

225
00:17:30,865 --> 00:17:34,185
I THINK IT'S WORTH
CHECKING OUT.

226
00:17:34,185 --> 00:17:37,788
[ Man On Phone ]
YO, MAN, LITTLE MONSTER'S "H"
AIN'T GONNA BE EASY.

227
00:17:37,788 --> 00:17:40,658
SEE, A LOT OF PEOPLE
RESPECTED HIM, YOU KNOW ?

228
00:17:40,658 --> 00:17:43,160
YOU BUYIN' OR NOT ?
YOU'RE NOT BUYIN',
I CAN GO TO SOMEBODY ELSE.

229
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:45,580
[ Laughing ]
NO, YOU CAN'T.

230
00:17:45,580 --> 00:17:48,416
BUT I'M FEELIN' MAGNANIMOUS.
SWING BY IN A COUPLE HOURS.

231
00:17:48,416 --> 00:17:51,919
MAYBE WE CAN DO
SOME BUSINESS.
GOOD.

232
00:17:51,919 --> 00:17:54,872
YEAH, THERE'S SOMETHIN'
I GOTTA LOOK INTO FIRST.

233
00:17:54,872 --> 00:17:57,341
WHEN I'M DONE,
I'LL BE IN TOUCH.

234
00:18:08,803 --> 00:18:12,006
[ Man ]
EYES WIDE, PLEASE, MARTY.
GOOD.

235
00:18:12,006 --> 00:18:14,458
TRY NOT TO MOVE
AROUND TOO MUCH.

236
00:18:16,444 --> 00:18:18,446
ARE YOU AWARE OF
ANY SENSATION AT ALL ?

237
00:18:18,446 --> 00:18:21,299
[ Gasps ]
IT'S A MIRACLE !

238
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:30,608
ALL RIGHT, MARTY,
NOW WE'RE GOING TO INTRODUCE
SOME OPTICAL STIMULI.

239
00:18:30,608 --> 00:18:32,310
TRY NOT TO BLINK.

240
00:18:39,967 --> 00:18:42,987
JUST RELAX FOR A MOMENT.

241
00:18:42,987 --> 00:18:47,325
I'M NOT GETTING ANYTHING.
I DON'T THINK THERE'S
ANY ACTIVITY...

242
00:18:47,325 --> 00:18:49,944
IN EITHER THE VISUAL CORTEX
OR THE SUPERIOR COLLICULUS.

243
00:18:50,444 --> 00:18:53,114
THERE'S NO WAY
THAT SHE COULD FOOL
THE MACHINE ?

244
00:18:53,114 --> 00:18:58,035
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT WHOLLY
INVOLUNTARY PHYSICAL RESPONSES.
I WASN'T GETTING ANY READING.

245
00:18:58,035 --> 00:18:59,937
THEN WHAT IS THAT ?

246
00:19:13,234 --> 00:19:16,020
[ Garbled Chatter ]

247
00:19:29,567 --> 00:19:31,819
WHAT IS IT, MARTY ?

248
00:19:31,819 --> 00:19:34,438
WHAT DO YOU SEE ?

249
00:19:36,073 --> 00:19:38,926
AGENTS.

250
00:19:48,452 --> 00:19:50,454
THIS IS DANIEL COSTA
FROM THE D.A.'S OFFICE.

251
00:19:50,955 --> 00:19:52,456
SO WHAT DID WE FIND ?

252
00:19:52,957 --> 00:19:55,208
I HEAR THE GIRL CAN ACTUALLY
SEE WITH SOME LIMITED ABILITY.

253
00:19:55,709 --> 00:19:57,210
NO, ACCORDING TO
HER EXAMINER,

254
00:19:57,711 --> 00:20:00,113
SHE IS COMPLETELY
WITHOUT SIGHT OR ANY KIND
OF LIGHT SENSITIVITY.

255
00:20:00,113 --> 00:20:02,699
BUT SHE IS STILL OUR BEST
AND ONLY SUSPECT.

256
00:20:02,699 --> 00:20:06,203
- YOU SAID YOU WERE
  MAKING PROGRESS.
- WE ARE.

257
00:20:06,203 --> 00:20:08,889
I'M NOT GONNA
INDICT A BLIND GIRL
ON SOME LOUSY PRINTS.

258
00:20:08,889 --> 00:20:11,675
SHE DOESN'T EXACTLY FIT
THE DEFINITION "BLIND GIRL."

259
00:20:11,675 --> 00:20:14,561
COME ON, FOLKS.
EITHER SHE IS OR SHE ISN'T.

260
00:20:14,561 --> 00:20:16,229
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT ?
- THERE IS EVIDENCE...

261
00:20:16,730 --> 00:20:19,950
OF SOME KIND OF NEUROLOGICAL
ACTIVITY WHICH CAUSED
HER PUPILS TO DILATE.

262
00:20:19,950 --> 00:20:23,236
- FROM WHAT ?
- TO ME IT INDICATES
  SOME REACTION TO STIMULI,

263
00:20:23,236 --> 00:20:26,106
SOME KIND OF PHYSICAL RESPONSE
TO IMAGES IN HER MIND'S EYE.

264
00:20:26,106 --> 00:20:29,743
HOW DOES THAT MAKE HER
THE KILLER ?
I DIDN'T SAY IT DID.

265
00:20:29,743 --> 00:20:31,962
KICK HER LOOSE.

266
00:20:31,962 --> 00:20:34,548
-[ Pennock ]  DANNY--
- I GOT NO CASE, PENNOCK.

267
00:20:34,548 --> 00:20:38,051
I DON'T BELIEVE THIS !
I'M NOT TRYING HER,
NOT WITHOUT A MURDER WEAPON.

268
00:20:38,051 --> 00:20:40,053
KICK HER LOOSE.

269
00:20:43,056 --> 00:20:44,558
WONDERFUL.  THANKS.

270
00:20:59,523 --> 00:21:01,525
THESE BETTER STILL BE 20s.

271
00:21:01,525 --> 00:21:05,262
NO, I REPLACED THEM WITH 50s
SINCE YOU'RE SO DAMN SWEET.

272
00:21:28,385 --> 00:21:30,887
WANNA HEAR THE LATEST ?
YES.

273
00:21:30,887 --> 00:21:34,891
DETECTIVE PENNOCK
RAN THE GLOVES FOR BLOOD TYPING
AND FOUND TWO DIFFERENT SAMPLES,

274
00:21:35,392 --> 00:21:38,895
ONE TYPE MATCHING
MARTY GLENN'S.
THERE WERE NO CUTS ON HER.

275
00:21:39,396 --> 00:21:41,898
ALL THE SAME,
I'M GONNA HAND-DELIVER THEM
TO THE LAB IN WASHINGTON...

276
00:21:42,399 --> 00:21:45,735
AND EXPEDITE A P.C.R.
TO SEE IF SHE'S A MATCH.
LOOK AT HER.

277
00:21:45,735 --> 00:21:49,356
DO YOU REALLY THINK
SHE'S CAPABLE ?

278
00:21:49,356 --> 00:21:52,125
I'LL LET YOU KNOW
AS SOON AS I GET
THE TEST BACK.

279
00:22:05,805 --> 00:22:07,791
[ Garbled Screams ]

280
00:22:10,594 --> 00:22:12,846
WHO CALLED ME LAST NIGHT ?

281
00:22:14,297 --> 00:22:16,800
WHO'S WATCHIN' ME ?
WHAT ?

282
00:22:17,300 --> 00:22:19,636
AAH !  I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT !

283
00:22:19,636 --> 00:22:24,040
YOU A COP ?  HMM ?
 YOU WEARIN' A WIRE ?
[ Screaming ]

284
00:22:24,040 --> 00:22:27,711
NO !  I'M NOT A COP !

285
00:22:27,711 --> 00:22:30,564
I NEED TO GET
TO SPRING STREET !

286
00:22:30,564 --> 00:22:33,483
WHICH WAY IS SPRING STREET !
SOMEBODY ANSWER ME !

287
00:22:33,984 --> 00:22:35,986
FOUR BLOCKS
TO THE LEFT.

288
00:22:40,190 --> 00:22:42,058
[ Horns Honking ]

289
00:23:01,494 --> 00:23:03,880
WHERE ?
[ Man ]  HERE, HERE.  THERE'S
AN ALLEY HERE.  RIGHT HERE.

290
00:23:05,382 --> 00:23:08,385
OKAY, I'M FINE, THANKS.
LEAVE ME ALONE.

291
00:24:07,711 --> 00:24:09,713
[ Marty ]
EXCUSE ME.

292
00:24:10,213 --> 00:24:11,715
EXCUSE ME, SOMEBODY.

293
00:24:18,722 --> 00:24:21,658
- YEAH ?
- I KILLED 'EM.

294
00:24:23,259 --> 00:24:25,562
I KILLED THEM BOTH.

295
00:24:39,625 --> 00:24:41,126
[ Door Opens ]

296
00:24:55,274 --> 00:24:57,076
I READ YOUR CONFESSION.

297
00:24:58,894 --> 00:25:02,831
DETECTIVE PENNOCK IS
TYPING IT UP AS WE SPEAK
FOR YOU TO SIGN.

298
00:25:05,217 --> 00:25:08,220
I'LL SIGN IT.
YOU'LL MAKE HIM
A VERY HAPPY MAN.

299
00:25:08,721 --> 00:25:10,222
CAN'T HAVE EVERYTHING.

300
00:25:10,222 --> 00:25:14,510
AS FOR ME, I'M A LITTLE PUZZLED
BY THIS SUDDEN CHANGE OF HEART.

301
00:25:14,510 --> 00:25:18,647
PLEASE.
TOO MUCH CHARITY OF HEART,
AND I'LL WANNA PUKE.

302
00:25:18,647 --> 00:25:22,901
I JUST--
WHY KILL THEM ?

303
00:25:22,901 --> 00:25:24,787
PACO ORDONEZ.
SUSAN FORESTER.

304
00:25:27,005 --> 00:25:29,792
DID YOU EVEN KNOW
THAT WAS HER NAME ?

305
00:25:30,292 --> 00:25:33,545
SUSAN FORESTER.
SHE WAS 30 YEARS OLD.
NATIVE OF WILMINGTON.

306
00:25:34,046 --> 00:25:36,548
SHE WAITRESSED PART-TIME.
SHE LIVED ALONE
WITH HER TWO CATS.

307
00:25:36,548 --> 00:25:38,450
SHUT UP !

308
00:25:43,389 --> 00:25:45,391
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS ?

309
00:25:45,391 --> 00:25:48,394
I-I-- I'VE GIVEN YOU PEOPLE
EVERYTHING YOU WANT.

310
00:26:02,808 --> 00:26:07,262
I LIKE YOU, MARTY.
 I ADMIRE YOU.

311
00:26:07,262 --> 00:26:10,299
AND I DON'T WANT TO SEE
YOU CONFESS TO CRIMES
YOU DIDN'T COMMIT.

312
00:26:10,299 --> 00:26:12,434
YOU JUST FEEL SORRY FOR ME.
NO, I DON'T.

313
00:26:12,434 --> 00:26:14,269
NOT THE WAY YOU THINK I DO.

314
00:26:14,269 --> 00:26:17,172
READ THE CONFESSION.
I GOT IT ALL PERFECT.

315
00:26:17,673 --> 00:26:20,509
EVERY DETAIL.
HOW COULD I DO THAT
IF I'M INNOCENT ?

316
00:26:20,509 --> 00:26:24,346
I BELIEVE YOU
WITNESSED BOTH MURDERS.
YOU-YOU SAW THEM SOMEHOW.

317
00:26:24,346 --> 00:26:28,584
BUT YOU WERE WAY ACROSS TOWN
WHEN THEY HAPPENED.
YOU WERE A $60 CAB RIDE AWAY.

318
00:26:28,584 --> 00:26:31,420
YOU'RE CRAZY.
I THINK YOU TRIED
TO STOP THEM.

319
00:26:31,420 --> 00:26:34,189
YOU TRIED TO, BUT YOU DIDN'T
GET THERE IN TIME.

320
00:26:38,594 --> 00:26:40,596
I DON'T HAVE TO
TALK TO YOU ANYMORE.

321
00:26:40,596 --> 00:26:46,502
MARTY, WHOEVER DID THIS,
THEY'RE GONNA KILL AGAIN,

322
00:26:46,502 --> 00:26:48,871
AND YOU CAN HELP STOP THAT.

323
00:26:53,358 --> 00:26:55,194
I CAN'T STOP ANYTHING.

324
00:26:59,598 --> 00:27:03,652
I DON'T HAVE TO TALK
TO YOU ANYMORE, PERIOD.
OFFICER !  WE'RE DONE !

325
00:27:03,652 --> 00:27:07,489
WHO'S WORTH PLEADING
GUILTY FOR, MARTY ?
OFFICER !  WE'RE DONE !

326
00:27:07,489 --> 00:27:09,725
YOU DIDN'T DO IT.

327
00:27:09,725 --> 00:27:12,444
AND I'M NOT GONNA
LET THIS HAPPEN.

328
00:27:14,179 --> 00:27:17,933
DO YOU HEAR ME ?
MARTY ?

329
00:27:25,641 --> 00:27:27,509
[ Man ]
SORRY, MAN, DEAL'S OFF.

330
00:27:28,010 --> 00:27:31,013
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"DEAL'S OFF" ?
YOU CAN'T BACK OUT.

331
00:27:31,013 --> 00:27:33,515
I DO WHAT I GOT TO DO
TO STAY ON THE DOWN-LOW.

332
00:27:33,515 --> 00:27:36,018
YOU'RE SHININ'
TOO MUCH LIGHT ON ME.

333
00:27:36,018 --> 00:27:38,020
WHAT ARE YOU TALKIN' ABOUT ?

334
00:27:38,020 --> 00:27:41,523
SOMEBODY'S GUNNIN' FOR YOU,
AND I AIN'T GETTIN'
IN THE MIDDLE OF IT.

335
00:27:41,523 --> 00:27:44,026
WHO ?
WHO'S GUNNIN' FOR ME ?

336
00:27:44,026 --> 00:27:49,031
SOME OLD GIRLFRIEND OF YOURS
CALLED LAST NIGHT AND TOLD ME
I SHOULD STEER CLEAR.

337
00:27:49,531 --> 00:27:52,034
SHE CALLED YOU ?
YEAH.

338
00:27:52,034 --> 00:27:54,536
SAID SHE WAS
PASSIN' THE WORD.

339
00:27:57,539 --> 00:28:00,042
LISTEN TO ME.
 LISTEN, MAN.

340
00:28:00,042 --> 00:28:04,046
SHE'S NOBODY.
SHE KNOWS NOTHIN'.
UH-HUH.  YEAH, RIGHT.

341
00:28:04,046 --> 00:28:08,550
YOU AND ME, MAN,
WE'RE STILL COOL.
TRUST ME.

342
00:28:08,550 --> 00:28:11,553
IF SHE DON'T KNOW ANYTHING,
HOW'D SHE GET THIS NUMBER ?

343
00:28:14,556 --> 00:28:18,560
LISTEN TO ME.
I GOT NOWHERE ELSE
TO TAKE THIS STUFF.

344
00:28:18,560 --> 00:28:20,562
THAT'S NOT MY PROBLEM.

345
00:28:20,562 --> 00:28:23,065
JUST DON'T YOU
CALL HERE AGAIN.
[ Line Disconnects ]

346
00:28:40,415 --> 00:28:42,551
[ Door Opens ]

347
00:28:44,853 --> 00:28:47,856
WELL, I APPRECIATE YOUR
HELP HERE, SUCH AS IT WAS,

348
00:28:47,856 --> 00:28:49,858
BUT I'D SAY WE'RE
DOING ALL RIGHT.

349
00:28:49,858 --> 00:28:53,211
SHE JUST SIGNED
HER CONFESSION.

350
00:28:53,211 --> 00:28:54,913
CONGRATULATIONS.

351
00:28:54,913 --> 00:28:57,316
I DON'T FEEL AS GOOD
AS YOU MIGHT THINK,
YOU KNOW.

352
00:28:57,316 --> 00:29:01,536
ALL YOU GOT IS A SIGNATURE.
NO LAWYER'S GONNA LET HER
GO DOWN BASED ON THAT.

353
00:29:01,536 --> 00:29:03,689
I'M AWARE OF THAT.

354
00:29:03,689 --> 00:29:06,909
DOESN'T IT BOTHER YOU,
DETECTIVE, THAT YOU STILL
HAVE NO CLEAR MOTIVE ?

355
00:29:06,909 --> 00:29:10,279
WELL, SHE JUST NOW
GAVE US THAT--

356
00:29:10,779 --> 00:29:12,281
DRUGS.

357
00:29:12,281 --> 00:29:14,650
JUST LIKE I THOUGHT.

358
00:29:14,650 --> 00:29:17,920
SHE EVEN TOLD US
WHERE TO FIND THEM.

359
00:29:33,351 --> 00:29:36,855
I'D THIS IS GONNA MAKE IT
A PRETTY SHORT TRIAL.

360
00:29:36,855 --> 00:29:39,357
IF YOU THINK ABOUT IT,
DETECTIVE, IT ACTUALLY
PROVES NOTHING.

361
00:29:39,357 --> 00:29:42,244
THERE IT IS,
JUST LIKE SHE SAID.
JUST LIKE SHE DESCRIBED.

362
00:29:42,244 --> 00:29:46,147
YOU KNOW, THE THING
I FIND MOST SURPRISING
ABOUT THIS CASE IS YOU.

363
00:29:46,147 --> 00:29:48,667
YOU ARE ONE SKEPTICAL GUY,
AGENT MULDER.

364
00:29:49,167 --> 00:29:51,052
SKEPTICAL ?
OH, YEAH.

365
00:29:51,052 --> 00:29:54,005
I'VE BEEN CALLED
A LOT OF THINGS.
"SKEPTICAL" IS NOT ONE.

366
00:29:54,005 --> 00:29:56,474
[ Cell Phone Ringing ]
YEAH, WELL, WHATEVER.

367
00:30:00,979 --> 00:30:02,480
[ Scoffs ]
SKEPTICAL.

368
00:30:02,480 --> 00:30:04,416
MULDER.
WHAT ?

369
00:30:04,916 --> 00:30:08,420
I'VE GOT THE P.C.R. RESULTS
ON THE TWO BLOOD TYPES
FROM THE GLOVES.

370
00:30:08,420 --> 00:30:11,423
NEITHER WAS MARTY'S.
YOU WERE RIGHT, MULDER.
SHE DIDN'T DO IT.

371
00:30:11,423 --> 00:30:14,392
I KNOW THAT, YOU KNOW THAT
AND SO DOES WHOEVER
MARTY'S PROTECTING,

372
00:30:14,392 --> 00:30:16,778
BUT PENNOCK IS
SALIVATING RIGHT NOW.

373
00:30:16,778 --> 00:30:19,047
WHAT WE HAVE TO DO
IS CONVINCE MARTY.

374
00:30:19,047 --> 00:30:21,533
I GOT AN IDEA.
I'LL GET BACK TO YOU.

375
00:30:49,894 --> 00:30:51,896
[ Footsteps Approaching ]

376
00:30:52,897 --> 00:30:55,266
WHAT DO YOU WANT NOW ?

377
00:31:09,998 --> 00:31:12,500
I KNOW WHO
YOU'RE PROTECTING, MARTY,

378
00:31:12,500 --> 00:31:14,502
AND I THINK I KNOW WHY.

379
00:31:16,504 --> 00:31:18,506
YOU'RE PROTECTING THE MAN
WHO MURDERED YOUR MOTHER.

380
00:31:18,506 --> 00:31:22,427
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

381
00:31:22,427 --> 00:31:25,430
I READ THE ORIGINAL
POLICE REPORT FROM 1970.

382
00:31:26,931 --> 00:31:30,435
YOUR MOTHER DIED FROM
A SINGLE STAB WOUND
TO THE RIGHT KIDNEY,

383
00:31:30,435 --> 00:31:35,423
AS DID PACO ORDONEZ
AND SUSAN FORESTER.

384
00:31:35,423 --> 00:31:38,176
DEAD AT THE HANDS OF
AN UNKNOWN ASSAILANT.

385
00:31:41,479 --> 00:31:44,482
I NEVER KNEW MY MOTHER.
NO.

386
00:31:44,482 --> 00:31:46,985
I KNOW.

387
00:31:46,985 --> 00:31:49,487
BUT FOR ONCE YOU WERE
THERE WHEN IT HAPPENED.

388
00:31:49,988 --> 00:31:53,241
SHE WAS PREGNANT
WITH YOU AT THE TIME.

389
00:31:53,241 --> 00:31:57,529
SHE DIED ON THE OPERATING TABLE
AS DOCTORS WERE TRYING
TO SAVE HER.

390
00:31:59,531 --> 00:32:03,034
YOU WERE BORN...
JUST BARELY.

391
00:32:04,536 --> 00:32:09,040
BUT THE INTERRUPTION OF
BLOOD FLOW YOU SUFFERED MOST
LIKELY CAUSED YOUR BLINDNESS.

392
00:32:10,041 --> 00:32:12,544
WHAT DOES THAT HAVE
TO DO WITH ANYTHING ?

393
00:32:13,545 --> 00:32:15,547
I THINK THAT
DURING THAT TIME...

394
00:32:17,966 --> 00:32:21,469
AS YOU LOST ONE SENSE...

395
00:32:21,469 --> 00:32:23,471
YOU GAINED ANOTHER.

396
00:32:24,973 --> 00:32:27,475
AND SOMEHOW...

397
00:32:27,976 --> 00:32:31,980
A CONNECTION WAS FORMED
BETWEEN YOU AND YOUR
MOTHER'S KILLER.

398
00:32:31,980 --> 00:32:34,816
WHAT CONNECTION ?
YOU SEE THROUGH HIS EYES.

399
00:32:36,718 --> 00:32:40,555
YOU ALWAYS HAVE.
YOU DON'T WANT TO,
YOU JUST DO.

400
00:32:40,555 --> 00:32:45,326
AND BECAUSE OF THAT YOU FEEL
RESPONSIBLE FOR HIS ACTIONS,
BUT YOU'RE NOT.

401
00:32:48,530 --> 00:32:51,032
AND YOU'RE SITTING HERE
IN PRISON...

402
00:32:51,032 --> 00:32:54,035
FOR CRIMES
YOU DIDN'T COMMIT.

403
00:32:54,035 --> 00:32:57,455
IT ISN'T GOING TO
ACCOMPLISH ANYTHING, MARTY.

404
00:32:57,455 --> 00:33:01,209
[ Footsteps Approaching ]
[ Pennock ]
EXCUSE ME, AGENT MULDER.

405
00:33:01,209 --> 00:33:05,196
SHE'S BEING
TRANSFERRED NOW.

406
00:33:05,196 --> 00:33:07,198
THERE'S ABSOLUTELY NO POINT
TO YOU DOING THIS.

407
00:33:07,198 --> 00:33:10,201
WE'RE GONNA FIND HIM
WITH OR WITHOUT YOUR HELP.

408
00:33:22,213 --> 00:33:24,215
I'M SORRY.

409
00:34:38,873 --> 00:34:41,325
[ Buzzing ]

410
00:34:41,826 --> 00:34:43,828
[ Guard ]
ALL RIGHT.

411
00:34:43,828 --> 00:34:45,996
[ Chattering ]

412
00:34:55,139 --> 00:34:57,141
HI, MARTY.

413
00:34:58,142 --> 00:35:00,144
WHAT'S GOING ON ?

414
00:35:00,144 --> 00:35:03,547
DETECTIVE PENNOCK IS
WITH THE WARDEN RIGHT NOW
ARRANGING FOR YOUR RELEASE.

415
00:35:03,547 --> 00:35:05,783
[ Groans ]
WHAT ?

416
00:35:05,783 --> 00:35:09,804
CHARGES AGAINST YOU ARE BEING
DROPPED.  YOU'RE NO LONGER
A SUSPECT IN THIS CASE.

417
00:35:09,804 --> 00:35:12,523
HOW CAN THEY DO THAT ?
I CONFESSED.

418
00:35:12,523 --> 00:35:16,026
A CONFESSION IS WORTHLESS
IF IT'S A LIE,
AND YOURS WAS A LIE.

419
00:35:16,026 --> 00:35:19,363
[ Sighs ]
WHAT HAVE YOU BEEN
TELLING THEM ?

420
00:35:19,363 --> 00:35:23,284
JUST THAT YOU'RE INNOCENT,
WHICH IS SOMETHING THEY WOULD'VE
FOUND OUT ON THEIR OWN ANYWAY.

421
00:35:23,284 --> 00:35:28,672
THE LOCKER YOU SENT US TO ?
IT HAD PRINTS ON IT,
BUT THEY WEREN'T YOURS.

422
00:35:28,672 --> 00:35:32,460
I WAS CAREFUL.
SOMEBODY ELSE
WASN'T SO CAREFUL.

423
00:35:32,460 --> 00:35:35,863
CHARLES WESLEY GOTTS,
AN EX-CON.

424
00:35:35,863 --> 00:35:38,866
CONVICTED IN 1970
OF AGGRAVATED ASSAULT.

425
00:35:39,366 --> 00:35:41,735
HE WAS PAROLED
THREE WEEKS AGO, AND HE'S
BEEN MISSING EVER SINCE.

426
00:35:41,735 --> 00:35:46,257
NEVER HEARD OF HIM.
I HAPPEN TO
BELIEVE THAT, MARTY.

427
00:35:46,257 --> 00:35:51,395
P.C.R. TEST CONFIRMED
THAT IT WAS HIS BLOOD
ON THE GLOVE.

428
00:35:53,898 --> 00:35:56,901
THE TEST CONFIRMED
SOMETHING ELSE, MARTY.

429
00:35:58,903 --> 00:36:00,888
HE'S YOUR FATHER.

430
00:36:11,732 --> 00:36:14,034
THAT WAS THE CONNECTION.

431
00:36:16,437 --> 00:36:18,439
HMM.

432
00:36:22,943 --> 00:36:26,614
[ Pennock ]
OKAY, WE'RE ALL SET.

433
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:33,304
THAT IS, IF EVERYTHING'S
TAKEN CARE OF ON THIS END.

434
00:36:35,639 --> 00:36:38,209
WHAT'S HE TALKIN' ABOUT ?

435
00:36:38,209 --> 00:36:41,495
DETECTIVE PENNOCK
HAS AGREED TO...

436
00:36:41,495 --> 00:36:45,366
NOT PURSUE AIDING
AND ABETTING CHARGES IF
YOU AGREE TO HELP US--

437
00:36:46,850 --> 00:36:49,353
IF YOU AGREE
TO HELP US FIND HIM.

438
00:36:50,738 --> 00:36:53,674
WE NEED YOUR HELP,
MARTY.

439
00:36:55,676 --> 00:36:57,678
YOU CAN END IT NOW.

440
00:37:01,148 --> 00:37:03,951
I CAN END THIS.

441
00:37:03,951 --> 00:37:07,121
I'M SURE THAT'S WHAT
YOU'VE ALWAYS WANTED.

442
00:37:13,010 --> 00:37:17,014
I NEVER WANTED TO SPEND MY LIFE
IN A PLACE LIKE THIS.

443
00:37:17,014 --> 00:37:19,016
I HAD NO CHOICE.

444
00:37:23,520 --> 00:37:25,522
HMM.

445
00:37:25,522 --> 00:37:28,325
IF I HELP YOU,
WILL YOU PROTECT ME
UNTIL HE'S CAUGHT ?

446
00:37:29,727 --> 00:37:32,229
I WILL PERSONALLY
GUARANTEE YOUR SAFETY.

447
00:37:34,465 --> 00:37:36,667
HMM.

448
00:37:36,667 --> 00:37:38,969
TAKE ME HOME.

449
00:37:51,265 --> 00:37:54,268
[ Man On Police Radio ]
MOVING INTO POSITION
AT THE BACK EXIT.

450
00:37:54,268 --> 00:37:57,171
- ALL RIGHT.  STAND BY.
-COPY THAT.

451
00:38:03,377 --> 00:38:05,379
JUST IN TIME
FOR THE SURPRISE PARTY.

452
00:38:05,379 --> 00:38:07,381
SHE TOLD YOU
HE'D BE IN THERE ?

453
00:38:07,381 --> 00:38:10,351
YEAH.  SHE DESCRIBED
THIS PLACE PERFECTLY,
RIGHT DOWN TO THE MATCHBOOKS.

454
00:38:10,351 --> 00:38:13,220
WHAT MADE HER
DECIDE TO COOPERATE ?
SHE WANTS TO STOP HIM.

455
00:38:13,220 --> 00:38:17,925
ALL OF A SUDDEN ?
WHY DIDN'T SHE TELL US
HIS NAME BEFORE NOW ?

456
00:38:17,925 --> 00:38:21,128
SHE DIDN'T KNOW HIS NAME.
THEY NEVER MET.  HE'S BEEN
IN PRISON HER ENTIRE LIFE.

457
00:38:21,128 --> 00:38:24,965
YET ACCORDING TO YOU,
SHE'S BEEN SEEING THROUGH
HIS EYES THE WHOLE TIME.

458
00:38:24,965 --> 00:38:28,035
I DON'T THINK SHE WAS SURE
EXACTLY WHAT SHE WAS SEEING.

459
00:38:28,035 --> 00:38:32,523
IT WAS MORE LIKE A CONSTANT
IMAGE IN HER MIND SHE LEARNED
TO LIVE WITH OVER TIME--

460
00:38:32,523 --> 00:38:35,075
UP UNTIL THREE WEEKS AGO.

461
00:38:35,075 --> 00:38:36,777
WHEN THE MURDERS STARTED.

462
00:38:36,777 --> 00:38:38,946
HE WAS PAROLED
AND EVERYTHING CHANGED.

463
00:38:38,946 --> 00:38:43,767
WELL, IF ALL THIS IS TRUE,
LET'S GO GET HIM.

464
00:38:46,253 --> 00:38:48,656
MULDER ?

465
00:38:51,425 --> 00:38:53,927
EVERYTHING'S CHANGED
FOR HER, SCULLY.

466
00:38:55,929 --> 00:38:58,899
I DON'T THINK WE'RE GONNA
FIND HIM IN THERE.

467
00:39:04,438 --> 00:39:07,241
NEED SOME HELP
OVER THERE ?
NO.

468
00:39:07,241 --> 00:39:09,243
SHOULDA KNOWN.

469
00:39:22,756 --> 00:39:25,759
NOW, YOU KNOW,
YOU DON'T HAVE TO PACK
EVERYTHING YOU OWN.

470
00:39:25,759 --> 00:39:29,763
I PROMISE YOU,
YOU'RE NOT GONNA BE IN
PROTECTIVE CUSTODY THAT LONG.

471
00:39:31,265 --> 00:39:34,551
IT'S TOO LATE
FOR THAT ANYWAY.
WHY'S THAT ?

472
00:39:34,551 --> 00:39:37,337
GOTTS IS ALREADY HERE.

473
00:39:40,758 --> 00:39:42,760
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKIN' ABOUT ?

474
00:39:45,979 --> 00:39:48,781
HE'S BEEN KEEPING TABS ON YOU
FOR ABOUT A DAY.

475
00:39:50,099 --> 00:39:52,118
NOW HE KNOWS WHERE I LIVE.

476
00:40:00,076 --> 00:40:01,911
HE'S READING THE NAMES
ON THE MAILBOXES RIGHT NOW.

477
00:40:01,911 --> 00:40:05,114
WHAT ?
HOW COULD YOU--

478
00:40:05,114 --> 00:40:06,949
[ Grunts ]

479
00:40:38,181 --> 00:40:40,600
HOW DID YOU KNOW HE
WOULDN'T BE IN THERE ?

480
00:40:40,600 --> 00:40:44,103
SHE MISDIRECTED US ON PURPOSE.
SHE'S STILL PROTECTING HIM ?

481
00:40:44,103 --> 00:40:46,105
NO, SHE'S NOT.
SHE NEVER WAS.

482
00:40:46,606 --> 00:40:49,275
PENNOCK'S NOT PICKING UP.
WHAT DO YOU MEAN ?

483
00:40:49,275 --> 00:40:52,779
IT'S NOT HIM SHE'S BEEN
PROTECTING.  IF HE GOES BACK
TO PRISON, SO DOES SHE.

484
00:40:53,279 --> 00:40:55,565
UNTIL NOW,
SHE'S NEVER HAD A CHOICE.

485
00:41:28,114 --> 00:41:30,450
[ Clicks ]

486
00:42:08,921 --> 00:42:12,675
[ Whispers ]
I HATE THE WAY YOU SEE ME.

487
00:42:23,519 --> 00:42:25,404
MULDER.

488
00:42:27,857 --> 00:42:31,644
SHE DID THIS ONE.
TRUST ME.

489
00:42:54,400 --> 00:42:59,705
NOT MUCH TO LOOK AT, IS IT ?
AT LEAST, THAT'S WHAT
THEY TELL ME.

490
00:43:11,934 --> 00:43:13,936
YOU WERE AT THE SENTENCING,
AGENT MULDER.

491
00:43:13,936 --> 00:43:18,241
IS IT MY COLOGNE ?
NO, I JUST KNEW
YOU'D BE THERE.

492
00:43:19,725 --> 00:43:21,727
MARTY, LET ME SPEAK TO
THE JUDGE ON YOUR BEHALF.

493
00:43:21,727 --> 00:43:23,629
NO.

494
00:43:28,885 --> 00:43:31,387
WE FOUND WHERE
HE'D BEEN STAYING.

495
00:43:31,387 --> 00:43:34,390
IT'S A MOTEL NOT FAR
FROM WHERE PACO ORDONEZ
HAD BEEN MURDERED.

496
00:43:34,891 --> 00:43:37,193
AND BEFORE THAT,
ATLANTIC CITY.

497
00:43:38,694 --> 00:43:42,198
HMM.  I'D NEVER SEEN
THE OCEAN BEFORE.

498
00:43:43,699 --> 00:43:45,701
AND NOW,
WHEN I CLOSE MY EYES,

499
00:43:45,701 --> 00:43:48,204
OR EVEN WHEN I OPEN THEM,

500
00:43:48,204 --> 00:43:50,206
THAT'S ALL I SEE.

501
00:43:55,628 --> 00:43:57,630
YOU'RE LUCKY HE WASN'T
A FAN OF THE ICE CAPADES.

502
00:43:58,130 --> 00:43:59,582
[ Chuckles ]

503
00:44:06,122 --> 00:44:08,474
[ Man On P.A. ]
LIGHTS OUT.

504
00:45:13,905 --> 00:45:16,476
[ Child ]
I MADE THIS !

